<note n="0863012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0863012">Tadyathā Oṁ he he bhagavaṁ, bahu-rūpa-dharaḥ divya-cakṣuṣe avalokya avalokya māṁ samya-manuamara kumāra-rūpa-dhāriṇe mahā-bodhisattva, kiṁ cirāyasi, hūṁ hūṁ phaṭ phaṭ svāhā.</note>
